Cocos2dxActivity `sContext` variable could cause memory leaked in Android App!
here is the leaked code:

``` java
public abstract class Cocos2dxActivity extends Activity implements Cocos2dxHelperListener {
    private static Cocos2dxActivity sContext = null;

    public static Context getContext() {
        return sContext;
    }
}
```

**Please do not use static strong reference Cocos2dxActivity object,instead your should use WeakReference<Cocos2dxActivity>.**
Please fix this memory leak issue as soon as possible!
